{"tid":2303797,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《全民造星III》│導師彭秀慧曾遭隊員質疑打擊:佢哋無必要信任我，我又唔係花姐","createTime":"2020-11-28T08:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T11:41:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9776548758ea5602083056441ef12c54bde3d7","tid":2303797,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"我天性係有啲mean<br />\nViuTV皇牌真人騷，《全民造星III》，以藝人再出道的主題，給有經驗表演者一個重新出發的機會。開播以來，一班參賽者都不及兩位導師彭秀慧同林二汶的火花搶fu，每每她們與花姐出場，都會變成主菜。<br />\n<br />\n尤其網民勁buy舞台劇出身的彭秀慧，說話一針見血，甚至愛她夠mean！<br />\n<br />\n「實在我唔知道咩嘢叫mean，希望係等如一針見血啦。但其實更加想啲人發現我係好鍾意講笑。」彭秀慧說。<br />\n<br />\n她重提面試其中一幕，有位女參加者萬事皆說:「阿媽話！」<br />\n<br />\n「我問佢點解唔叫阿媽嚟參加？對我嚟講，都可能有少少mean，但其實都只係想搞笑。例如有睇過《29+1》舞台劇的話，有一段係我同觀眾傾偈，其實我嘅mean已經流露咗出嚟，我就會寸遲到嘅人。當時我同另一邊觀眾講緊嘢嘅時候，見到有位女觀眾慢慢行去坐喺第一行，於是我講完之後，就走過去同佢講:『唔好以為我見唔到你！』，跟手問佢係咪好趕？食飯遲咗定係其他原因？跟住佢話嚟到劇院嘅時候已經閂門，即係其實佢已經遲咗。我嘅急才就係會話:『你覺得閂門係你唔啱定係佢唔啱呢？』跟住就全場爆笑。可能坐喺度嗰個人會覺得我好mean，但其實我只係為效果，而呢啲說話會自動喺個腦走出嚟。好啦算啦！我嘅天性都係有啲mean嘅！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_768005_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_768005_0&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CuzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=89a997fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_768005_0&h=d011253c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_768005_0</a>"},{"pid":"c2e48fbcbfceba983056f68ef9088d91db6ac17c","tid":2303797,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">全民造馬</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c30eb9d180fe3d285db3815688651cd2907cb2","tid":2303797,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}